item.description:
This month, Diane Arrigo. D.C of Chiropractic Health will be presenting her Chiropractic Practice Specialty and her goals, concerns, and issues. The other members of the group will provide feedback and recommendations to help her address any questions she may have.
The meeting is confidential and all disclosures therein are meant solely for the use of the participants and should not be shared outside of the group without the express consent and permission of the presenter.
All participants agree to maintain the strict confidentiality of any proprietary information that may be disclosed by members to the group. This is not a networking event and all members are expected to respect this policy.
Thank you very much.
